{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"iddb35c1e8-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s350"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"350"},"text":"§ 350.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Purchase and sale of debentures and like obligations of intermediate credit banks and agricultural credit corporations","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Any Federal reserve bank may also buy and sell debentures and other such obligations issued by a Federal intermediate credit bank or by a national agricultural credit corporation, but only to the same extent as and subject to the same limitations as those upon which it may buy and sell bonds issued under title I of the Federal Farm Loan Act.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"iddb35c1e9-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1913-12-23/ch6/s13A"},"text":"Dec. 23, 1913, ch. 6, § 13A","children":[],"tail":" (par.), formerly § 13a, as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1923-03-04/ch252"},"text":"Mar. 4, 1923, ch. 252","children":[],"tail":", title IV, § 404, "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/42/1480"},"text":"42 Stat. 1480","children":[],"tail":"; renumbered § 13A, "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/242/tI/s142/e/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–242, title I, § 142(e)(1)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1991-12-19"},"text":"Dec. 19, 1991","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/105/2281"},"text":"105 Stat. 2281","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"iddb35c1ea-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"iddb35c1eb-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"iddb35c1ec-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Title I of the Federal Farm Loan Act, referred to in text, is title I of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1916-07-17/ch245"},"text":"act July 17, 1916, ch. 245","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/39/360"},"text":"39 Stat. 360","children":[],"tail":". Title I was classified to chapter 7 (§ 641 et seq.) of this title, and was repealed by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/92/181/tV/s5"},"text":"Pub. L. 92–181, title V, § 5","children":[],"tail":".26(a), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1971-12-10"},"text":"Dec. 10, 1971","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/85/624"},"text":"85 Stat. 624","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"iddb35c1ed-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Codification","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section is comprised of third par. of section 13A, formerly section 13a, as added ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1923-03-04"},"text":"Mar. 4, 1923","children":[],"tail":". Pars. 1, 2, 4 and 5 of section 13A are set out as sections 348, 349, 351 and 352 of this title, respectively."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"iddb35c1ee-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"miscellaneous","id":"iddb35c1ef-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"National Agricultural Credit Corporation","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Title II of the Agricultural Credits Act, act ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1923-03-04"},"text":"Mar. 4, 1923","children":[],"tail":", title II, §§ 201–217, "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/42/1461"},"text":"42 Stat. 1461","children":[],"tail":", authorized creation of national agricultural credit corporations, prior to repeal by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/86/230"},"text":"Pub. L. 86–230","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1959-09-18"},"text":"Sept. 18, 1959","children":[],"tail":", § 24, "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/73/466"},"text":"73 Stat. 466","children":[],"tail":". Prior to such repeal, act "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1933-06-16"},"text":"June 16, 1933","children":[],"tail":", § 77, "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/48/292"},"text":"48 Stat. 292","children":[],"tail":", had prohibited the creation, after "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1933-06-16"},"text":"June 16, 1933","children":[],"tail":", of national agricultural credit corporations authorized to be formed under the Agricultural Credits Act."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
